'''Armand Kajangwe''', ni [[Rwanda|umunyarwanda]] - umukinnyi wa firime wo mu Busuwisi . Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime nka ''The Asylum'', na ''Dirty Singles''<ref name=":0">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/200021</ref> .<ref>https://www.cmu.edu/ini/news/2020/alain-feature-2020.html</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Ku ya 7 Mata 2009, Kajangwe yinjiye mu isosiyete ikora ibicuruzwa byuzuye yitwa 'Crooked Seas Inc.' yashinzwe na Craig Leblanc ifite icyicaro i Ontario, muri [[Kanada]]<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/Armand_Kajangwe</ref>. Yakoze nk'umuyobozi, umuyobozi w'amafoto, n'umuyobozi ushinzwe imbuga nkoranyambaga.<ref>https://theculturetrip.com/africa/rwanda/articles/11-rwandan-filmmakers-you-need-to-know-about/</ref> 

Muri 2016, Kajangwe yagize uruhare mu gutangiza urubuga rwa mbere rwa videwo muri [[Afurika]]<ref>https://www.ktpress.rw/2021/08/students-to-win-prizes-in-a-new-tv-show/</ref>. Ihuriro rizwi ku izina rya 'www.journal.rw' ryatunganijwe kandi rikoreshwa na Village Innovation , uruganda ruhanga ruherereye mu [[Rwanda]] aho Kajangwe ari umuyobozi mukuru<ref name=":0" />. Ihuriro rirashobora gutanga inzira yo gusangira ibisobanuro bihanitse bya videwo<ref>https://rwanda.shafaqna.com/FR/AL/228004</ref>. 

